Your method of controlling the list is the most selfish and arrogant thing I have ever seen. The only purpose the &quot;maybe&quot; current rotation serves (assuming it hasn't gone FFA yet) is the larger guilds. They don't have to wait 8-10 months to get epic drops. They have to wait maybe a month (assuming a couple of patches) to get a shot at it.<br>
