<br>
Rotation does not help the larger guilds.  It does not help the smaller guilds either.<br>
<br>
Rotation helps guilds who have most of their players on PST.  A guild like IB for example would benefit from a rotation.  FFA would be harder for IB unless they get more European or EST members.   CJ, who is on CET would not benefit from a rotation as they have 90% of their guild online just after a patch.  FFA is better for a guild like CJ or Asura because they can pretty much have their pick of what mobs to slay right after a patch.  <br>
<br>
Its not a larger or small thing, its a timezone issue.<br>
